metadata.name: Germany DIE MANNSCHAFT
metadata.description: This artwork is inspired by Germany, its colors, landscapes, and football culture. The work seeks to portray the essence of this country and its history through the World Cup, as well as the iconic moments of each World Cup won throughout its history. Germany has won the 1954, 1974, 1990 and the 2014 World Cups.
